1. Should not call the endpoint if search text in blank, but prompt the user to enter text.
2. serach text should only be alphabets.
3. Search text can be multiple space separated words.
4. valid search text should fetch results on enter key press.
5. If not results are found, then the same should be shown on the UI.
6. If there is a data parsing error then the user should be prompted to try again.
7. When the results are populated ans a word is clicked, it should be inserted at the point where the cursor is.
8. The synonym lookup popup should closed once the text is inserted into the editor.